{"tid":1647374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔通香港真係挽完，移民係唯一既出路？","createTime":"2019-10-11T17:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T11:39:47.000Z","uid":194543,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9ff9e7efeb78c83c90dae2d9a379ea1ba30820","tid":1647374,"uid":194543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"我兩老本身係反送中之前就已經係好黃，一直打算移民，可惜我係97回歸之後出世，又過左依親既年齡，最近香港搞成甘，我老豆就好絕望，要我快啲走先，想我去台灣讀書之後移民過去，但係我成日覺得台灣讀書好似冇乜認受性，而且最重要既係我唔捨得香港，我覺得係呢個緊要關頭走左去好自私，但我都明香港一係就長期鬥爭，一係就挽完。所以而家真係好煩，又要煩香港又要煩自己。<br />\n唔通我地真係挽完，真係冇得救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb7598ec82622290c15a6a325ac1eec21edf77c","tid":1647374,"uid":118125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"有得走就好離開香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67551ddb4c09de1bc0e1a74e3f1f1a708ec843d3","tid":1647374,"uid":201414,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:15:05.000Z","msg":"挽你老母 食屎啦放負撚 祝樓主全家仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f02db7897a9030de5c648892fc77a702c1eb323","tid":1647374,"uid":194543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cb7598ec82622290c15a6a325ac1eec21edf77c","tid":1647374,"uid":118125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"有得走就好離開香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"但係真係唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f641b70144a0a8a65d18f0e8784a29a66ec796","tid":1647374,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLCPmok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLCPmok.jpg&h=d80cc8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話要爭取國際線支持，我依家開左個英文版連儂牆啦，全部同我入去瘋狂貼文宣!<br />\n<br />\n[English] LIHKG Lennon Wall ver 1.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640768\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640768</a>"},{"pid":"ed1190ad9668242c644156f5ef9374bdccc28304","tid":1647374,"uid":34336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c152369c5ecde4a08eb16130144d4d6dd19f0db","tid":1647374,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"去中國台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8be7194867ba0ebb33ec796c73f002d14ec84ce","tid":1647374,"uid":204306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"挽你老母"},{"pid":"dd923bb46a26befcd3566284c95386d8bd6fd9bf","tid":1647374,"uid":135798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:20:17.000Z","msg":"呢個post真係玩完"},{"pid":"6617249e017cf0398934a3ee53d1d7aca26f5392","tid":1647374,"uid":194543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed1190ad9668242c644156f5ef9374bdccc28304","tid":1647374,"uid":34336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cb7598ec82622290c15a6a325ac1eec21edf77c","tid":1647374,"uid":118125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"有得走就好離開香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"抗爭成功之後都要好長時間先會變翻以前甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc538d3d6a86d3ca9c02e261e29d024113e1f7a8","tid":1647374,"uid":194543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c152369c5ecde4a08eb16130144d4d6dd19f0db","tid":1647374,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":